message.content: Ho qala, ho lokela ho qala ho qhekellwa ho na le li-database tse nang le boitsebiso bo bobebe ka ho etsa thupelo ea kamoo. Ka ho qala, re tla fumana boiphihlelo ba ho qhekellwa ho na le li-database tse nang le boitsebiso bo bobebe. Ka mor'a le ho fumana boiphihlelo, re tla qhekella tse ling tse qhobosheane tsa ho qhekellwa ho na le li-database tse nang le boitsebiso bo bobebe ka ho etsa thupelo ea kamoo. Haeba u na le tšebeletso ea ho qhekella li-database tse nang le boitsebiso bo bobebe, ka kopo o re thusa ka ho fana ka boemo ba ho qhekella li-database tse nang le boitsebiso bo bobebe.
